{"tid":873407,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"范國威投共獲回報: 梁君彥批准向港鐵提出急切口頭質詢","createTime":"2018-10-23T12:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T12:49:20.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"378b16d7b54e2e0e13dcefd376134405a87d74fa","tid":873407,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:00:57.000Z","msg":"投共之後果然唔同d<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1424418-20181023.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1424418-20181023.htm&d=e4tGR7Q8S%2F3RfslG5nu8gUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=c6909e0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1424418-20181023.htm&h=646a25e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1424418-20181023.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n梁君彥批准范國威明天立會提港鐵4綫故障急切口頭質詢<br />\n2018-10-23 HKT 18:55<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會主席梁君彥批准新民主同盟范國威明日在立法會大會上，就上星期港鐵出現4綫故障提出急切口頭質詢，亦是梁君彥在今屆立法會會期首次批准議員在大會提出急切口頭質詢。<br />\n<br />\n范國威提出的急切質詢，包括關注港鐵正逐步更換各鐵路綫的信號系統，政府及港鐵會否立即採取措施，防止工程引致鐵路服務受阻，以及會否從速制訂緊急應變方案，以應付鐵路服務大規模受阻的情況。運輸及房屋局局長陳帆將出席回應議員提問。<br />\n<br />\n內會上星期五曾討論是否支持在明日大會會議，就港鐵今次事故提出急切口頭質詢，在民主派、工聯會、新民黨及議員何君堯支持下，最終以28票贊成、26票反對通過。"},{"pid":"8f19510e9ea923452d8c78937eee45cbe0d4fc33","tid":873407,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:06:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/EkS5xYv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEkS5xYv.png&h=c9b3b156&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53b38b40706ae738b3a73e79ea293a27b6cc0344","tid":873407,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:26:48.000Z","msg":"自己人"},{"pid":"4aca47c5dd18e8dbfbe441e69bc9e2ee410aeaa4","tid":873407,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T12:36:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以搵番當日佢多謝高登仔幅圖鞭屍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\